251
00:14:14,889 --> 00:14:16,217
What do you want for them?

252
00:14:16,291 --> 00:14:18,757
I'll tell you what I'll do.
You look like a nice guy.

253
00:14:18,927 --> 00:14:20,858
A thousand dollars for the deuce.

254
00:14:21,362 --> 00:14:23,760
