- Why wouldn't I know his name?

279
00:15:27,729 --> 00:15:30,491
- I never told you his name.
- I never told you his name.

280
00:15:31,232 --> 00:15:33,527
- Who are we talking about here?
- Joe Davola.

281
00:15:33,601 --> 00:15:36,033
Right, Joe Davola.

282
00:15:36,671 --> 00:15:38,329
How do you know his name?

283
00:15:38,806 --> 00:15:43,275
