They landed in Philadelphia.

363
00:20:01,936 --> 00:20:04,869
So what? They don't have another
plane? She couldn't take a bus?

364
00:20:04,939 --> 00:20:07,439
She's coming in tomorrow.
But I made it.

365
00:20:07,508 --> 00:20:09,735
Yeah. How about that? You made it.

366
00:20:09,810 --> 00:20:13,209
I'm so excited. Now we get to see
the opera together.

367
00:20:13,281 --> 00:20:16,873
We get to go to the opera...
Get out of here... Together.

368
00:20:16,951 --> 00:20:19,542
- Who's that?
- That's, that's Harry Fong.

369
00:20:19,620 --> 00:20:22,314
He's a very good friend of mine.
He's a big opera buff.

370
00:20:22,390 --> 00:20:25,152
Enjoy the show there, Harry!

371
00:20:25,293 --> 00:20:28,294
- Come on. Let's go.
- You know what?

372
00:20:28,362 --> 00:20:30,953
- Come on. You gotta let us in.
- Not without tickets.

373
00:20:31,032 --> 00:20:32,997
We have tickets. Just not with us.

374
00:20:33,067 --> 00:20:36,068
Well, that's a problem. Excuse me.

375
00:20:36,571 --> 00:20:39,139
