377
00:20:42,310 --> 00:20:44,810
Oh, that's rich.

378
00:20:44,879 --> 00:20:47,106
Clear the way so people
with tickets can pass.

379
00:20:47,181 --> 00:20:49,146
- We're with him.
- Are you guys ready?

380
00:20:49,217 --> 00:20:50,875
- Yes. Yes.
- Have you seen George?

381
00:20:50,952 --> 00:20:53,520
- We thought he was with you.
